name: Milla 90... The moment
description:
An iconic moment of the legendary Cameroon striker Roger Milla celebrating one of his goals in the italia 90 world cup finals. 


As a kid it was my first world cup that I watched from start to finish and I copied this celebration after scoring a goal on park kickabouts later that summer. 
From that moment was named Milla as a nickname which stuck with me for the next 8 years during my time living in my hometown.
